00:22:22.700 --> 00:22:25.830 align:middle line:90%
She wants to be a member.

00:22:25.830 --> 00:22:30.040 align:middle line:84%
HARDCASTLE WRIGHT: I have people
who contact me with emails.

00:22:30.040 --> 00:22:33.079 align:middle line:84%
