is part of the mission--

00:22:52.011 --> 00:22:53.510 align:middle line:10%
NOORY: Which is
part of what you do.

00:22:53.510 --> 00:22:55.100 align:middle line:10%
HARDCASTLE WRIGHT: Which
is part of the Institute

00:22:55.100 --> 00:22:56.190 align:middle line:10%
