00:22:56.190 --> 00:22:57.500 align:middle line:90%
Find a group.

00:22:57.500 --> 00:23:00.960 align:middle line:84%
Learn the language,
because sometimes we're

00:23:00.960 --> 00:23:03.450 align:middle line:84%
