but we've blocked it

00:23:03.450 --> 00:23:05.640 align:middle line:84%
because we don't have the
language to talk about it.

00:23:05.640 --> 00:23:08.690 align:middle line:84%
We're creating
language right now.

00:23:08.690 --> 00:23:10.290 align:middle line:84%
The Institute for
Exoconsciousness

00:23:10.290 --> 00:23:11.560 align:middle line:90%
is creating language.

00:23:11.560 --> 00:23:14.620 align:middle line:84%
ET experiencer groups
is creating language.

00:23:14.620 --> 00:23:17.510 align:middle line:84%
Word is very important
because that's

00:23:17.510 --> 00:23:21.760 align:middle line:84%
how we frame and give reality
to what's happening to us.

00:23:21.760 --> 00:23:23.940 align:middle line:84%
