technology implants.

00:24:25.080 --> 00:24:28.070 align:middle line:84%
For ET experiencers,
it means moving out

00:24:28.070 --> 00:24:29.900 align:middle line:84%
into that field
of consciousness.

00:24:29.900 --> 00:24:35.010 align:middle line:84%
And I think within religion,
within different times,

00:24:35.010 --> 00:24:37.190 align:middle line:84%
there's been almost
like tsunamis

00:24:37.190 --> 00:24:38.550 align:middle line:90%
