00:24:38.550 --> 00:24:40.520 align:middle line:84%
And we're in a
big one right now.

00:24:40.520 --> 00:24:43.270 align:middle line:84%
NOORY: To someone who
does not tap into this,

00:24:43.270 --> 00:24:47.830 align:middle line:84%
